high_descs: Walk forward to the door, then turn left, walk forward to the wall, then turn left to face the kitchen counter.
Pick up the butter knife that is on the counter.
Turn around completely, then right, walk to the end of the counter, turn right, then right again, then left and walk up to the kitchen sink.
Slice the tomato on the left that is in the kitchen sink.
Put the knife down in the sink.
Pick up a tomato slice out of the sink.
Turn to your left and walk up to the microwave that is on the counter in front of you.
Heat the slice of tomato in the microwave before taking it out and closing the door.
Turn around completely, move forward a few steps, then turn to the left to face the kitchen sink.
Place the slice of tomato in the kitchen sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated slice of tomato in the kitchen sink.

high_descs: Turn left around the kitchen counter and face the counter area where the butterknife is.
Pick up the butterknife on the counter.
Turn left and walk around the counter to go to the sink.
Slice the left-most tomato in the sink.
Place the butterknife in the sink.
Pick up a slice of the tomato in the sink.
Turn left and move to face the microwave.
Open the microwave, put the tomato slice inside and heat it for a moment, then take the tomato slice back out.
Turn around and go back to the sink.
Place the heated tomato slice in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated tomato slice in the sink.

high_descs: Move forward, turn right and face the counter on your left.
Take the silver knife from the counter in front of you.
Turn left then face the sink on your right.
Slice the tomato in the sink in front of you.
Place the knife in the sink in front of you.
Take a tomato slice from the sink in front of you.
Turn left and face the microwave in front of you.
Heat up the tomato slice in the microwave in front of you and take it out.
Turn around and face the sink on your left.
Place the tomato slice in the sink in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Place a warm tomato slice in the sink.
